&lt;p data-start=&quot;1344&quot; data-end=&quot;1443&quot;&gt;Prospect, qualify, and close new freight forwarder accounts aligned to our ideal customer profile&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1444&quot; data-end=&quot;1535&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1446&quot; data-end=&quot;1535&quot;&gt;Build and manage a strong outbound pipeline via calls, email, networking, and referrals&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1536&quot; data-end=&quot;1623&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1538&quot; data-end=&quot;1623&quot;&gt;Conduct consultative discovery to understand operational needs and buying processes&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1624&quot; data-end=&quot;1713&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1626&quot; data-end=&quot;1713&quot;&gt;Develop proposals, pricing strategies, and service plans that drive profitable growth&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1714&quot; data-end=&quot;1795&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1716&quot; data-end=&quot;1795&quot;&gt;Own the sales process from first contact through first shipment stabilization&lt;/p&gt;
